      <title>英国央行首席经济学家表示他对降息持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/boe-chief-economist-says-uk-is-getting-closer-to-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行首席经济学家休·皮尔表示，他在决定何时降息时过于谨慎，称官员们需要对通胀持续存在的风险保持警惕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/boe-chief-economist-says-uk-is-getting-closer-to-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:24:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
