      <title>德国调查房地产价值“一尘不染”的银行债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-probes-spotless-bank-bonds-over-real-estate-values</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国金融监管机构 BaFin 正在密切关注贷方用来担保 Pfandbriefe 担保债券的房地产，这个 4000 亿欧元的市场传统上被认为是最安全的信贷市场之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/germany-probes-spotless-bank-bonds-over-real-estate-values</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 11:02:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着盈利成为焦点，股票期货上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着财报季最繁忙的一周积聚动力，美国股指期货出现波动，持续上涨的希望取决于大型科技公司能否证明受人工智能热潮启发的高估值是合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 22:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
