      <title>迈阿密机场债券评级因航班需求旺盛而上调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/miami-airport-bond-rating-raised-on-booming-demand-for-flights</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人口激增刺激了对来自南佛罗里达州的航班的需求，周一标准普尔全球评级将迈阿密国际机场的信用评级提升一级至 A+。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/miami-airport-bond-rating-raised-on-booming-demand-for-flights</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 20:33:40 GMT</pubDate>
